- Request / Response Cycle

- Client / Server
    - Client: Browser
    - Server: Computer somewhere else

- Model / View / Controller 
    - Models: Ruby models (ActiveRecord)
    - Views: HTML templates
    - Controllers: Processes the requests and package up response using model and view info

- REST
    - REpresentational State Transfer
    - shows where we are

- Get vs Post
    - Get:  Gets information from server
    - Post: Sends information to the server